    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <h3><a name="Description"></a><b>Description</b></h3>

<p>On the iOS app, none of the links are responding or opening except the ePsule feature link. This prevents users from accessing other features and affects overall usability.</p>

<h3><a name="StepstoReproduce"></a><b>Steps to Reproduce</b></h3>

<ol>
	<li>Open the FP Agent App on an iOS device</li>
	<li>Navigate to the home/dashboard screen</li>
	<li>Tap on any feature link (e.g., Add Money, Transfer Money, Cash Collection)</li>
	<li>Observe the behavior</li>
	<li>Tap on the ePsule link</li>
</ol>


<h3><a name="ExpectedResult"></a><b>Expected Result</b></h3>

<p>All feature links should be clickable and navigate to their respective pages.</p>

<h3><a name="ActualResult"></a><b>Actual Result</b></h3>

<p>Only the ePsule link is working; all other links are unresponsive.</p>

<h3><a name="Severity"></a><b>Severity</b></h3>

<p>Critical</p>
            <br/>
        </td>
